; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　正如其名，技嘉GV-N650OC的频率比公版更高，达到1111MHz（频率很光棍），另外显卡使用了10CM大口径风扇，保证较高频率情况下都有较低温度。显卡外观和参数清楚了，我们来看看显卡拆解，到底技嘉对主流显卡的做工又如何呢？</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">技嘉GV-N650OC拆解：</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img title=\"技嘉GV-N650OC\" alt=\"技嘉GV-N650OC\" src=\"http://pai5.qpic.cn/paipai/LJdqCrSsydAvUXKs2kZD7XSpyCzDbRfkKQHHbXib0eW4/2000\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; width: 500px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; border-right: black 1px solid; padding-top: 0px\" /></a><br />\r\n拆解一览，简单四口螺丝固定</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img title=\"技嘉GV-N650OC\" alt=\"技嘉GV-N650OC\" src=\"http://pai2.qpic.cn/paipai/DISINfiaviaNdib3OB4oO92MjH9XZW9O3gkz5lMbeCU3lw/2000\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; width: 500px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; border-right: black 1px solid; padding-top: 0px\" /></a><br />\r\n散热器，依然纯铝制</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　显卡拆解颇为简单，四颗螺丝足够固定。显卡虽然使用了10CM大口径散热风扇，但散热鳍片还是比较稀疏，似乎散热效果一般，不过GTX650的核心温度本来不高，不需要夸张的散热器。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img title=\"技嘉GV-N650OC\" alt=\"技嘉GV-N650OC\" src=\"http://pai1.qpic.cn/paipai/JG20S5ia3J3Nd6Bia0RKktRoqmuX1oz2Ij7tjpic64n82k/2000\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; width: 500px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; border-right: black 1px solid; padding-top: 0px\" /></a><br />\r\nPCB板，用料比公版更优秀</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　技嘉GV-650OC的PCB板用料并不丰富，但算得上扎实，原件比公版更丰满，相数字供电，元件焊接等做工工整。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img title=\"技嘉GV-N650OC\" alt=\"技嘉GV-N650OC\" src=\"http://pai1.qpic.cn/paipai/FIxTiaqAFLhalyV1YmAX10ib9iaCHgNqgRVsLk0oApx2IA/2000\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; width: 500px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; border-right: black 1px solid; padding-top: 0px\" /></a><br />\r\n视讯接口也都有屏蔽措施</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><br />\r\n更优质的MOS</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　公版的Mosfet是常规Dpak封装的型号，而技嘉使用的这种Mosfet可以承受更高的温度，通过更多的电流，电感也采用了独家的Metal Choke，降低啸叫，提供耐温和电流通过力。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img title=\"技嘉GV-N650OC\" alt=\"技嘉GV-N650OC\" src=\"http://pai2.qpic.cn/paipai/iaS8NWoMwVibs419ZVzbyK3omCg4qxDDATt7L53WplR54/2000\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; width: 500px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; border-right: black 1px solid; padding-top: 0px\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img title=\"技嘉N650OC\" alt=\"技嘉N650OC\" src=\"http://pai6.qpic.cn/paipai/zaNSNCk9mMAaWhsrK8fncfTZQm4JuTuUWVF7Xt6Hr8o/2000\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; width: 245px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; border-right: black 1px solid; padding-top: 0px\" /></a><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img title=\"技嘉N650OC\" alt=\"技嘉N650OC\" src=\"http://pai1.qpic.cn/paipai/xrPesRfBCjZicItRXG2ISRc1bNR7XKJ3Poeh6QkibKibDY/2000\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; width: 245px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; border-right: black 1px solid; padding-top: 0px\" /></a><br />\r\nGPU核心和显存核心</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　技嘉GV-N650OC-1G所采用的GK107核心，采用台积电28nm工艺制造，核心频率达到1111MHz，比公版频率更高。显存方面选用了GDDR5显存，实际效能频率达5GHz，整卡的位宽为128bit。到底这样的规格参数会有怎样的性能？下面我们把显卡装到平台上测试一番。。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em