orm: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255,0,0)\">2012变形虎克盘 弯头180度旋转设计更加出色：<a href=\"http://item.taobao.com/item.htm?id=14629601246\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\">http://item.taobao.com/item.htm?id=14629601246</a></span></strong></span></span></div>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">产品速度只提供参考，具体以实物为准</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">PNY是美国通路市场第一大品牌，其<font style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51)\">U盘</font>产品种类丰富品质优良，深受全球用户的欢迎。近日PNY再次推出了新品&mdash;&mdash;虎克盘。这款U盘采用业界独创的勾头设计，盘体用高品质钢材打造，便携性与实用性非常突出，值得广大消费者关注。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img align=\"absMiddle\" src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/704326707/T2nIdrXhFMXXXXXXXX_!!704326707.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">PNY虎克盘的命名源自英文单词&ldquo;hook&rdquo;（即钩子的意思），其最大的特色就在于U盘的头部设计成钩子的形状，便于用户随身携带。PNY虎克盘的外观设计也是一大亮点，典雅的香槟色钢制外壳能够体现出使用者的非凡品位，表面除了PNY LOGO和容量标识外再无其他修饰，简约大方。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img align=\"absMiddle\" src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/704326707/T2ssXrXgNMXXXXXXXX_!!704326707.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">PNY虎克盘的尺寸为5.0mm高*15.8mm宽*48.6mm长，设计插拔方便，无丢盖之忧。结构上PNY虎克盘顶部的勾头是其最醒目的标志，为了保证U盘钩挂后不掉落，勾子下方还设计有一个圆柱形的插栓。钩挂物体时将插栓向外拔出，钩挂后插栓复位，勾头呈封闭状态，不必担心U盘掉落。这样一来U盘就可以轻松挂扣在钥匙包或链绳上，方便用户将存储的资料随身携带。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img align=\"absMiddle\" src=\"http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/704326707/T2o3pKXhxXXXXXXXXX_!!704326707.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">由于整个盘体都采用了高品质的钢材打造，PNY虎克盘不但看起来质感强烈，给人一种精工细作的好感。而且相比塑料材质的普通U盘更加坚固耐用，历久弥新。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img align=\"absMiddle\" src=\"http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/704326707/T2XcXrXf0MXXXXX