个插栓。钩挂物体时将插栓向外拔出，露出勾头的缺口；钩挂后再将插栓复位，勾头呈封闭状态，防止U盘掉落。这样勾型头配合圆柱形的插栓可轻松将U盘挂扣在钥匙包或链绳上，既美观又方便用户随身携带。</div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 由于整个盘体都采用了高品质的钢材打造，PNY虎克盘不但看起来质感强烈，给人一种精工细作的好感。而且相比塑料材质的普通U盘更加坚固耐用，历久弥新。性能方面，PNY虎克盘采用优质存储芯片，提供4GB、8GB、16GB和32GB四种容量。支持windows 7，Mac OS：10.3 above等最新操作系统，质保期长达五年。另外得益于全金属的外壳设计，PNY虎克盘坚固耐用，能够防止意外造成的盘体损坏和数据损失。</div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;HOOK---很酷，很坚固，很迷你！<img src=\"http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/612263230/T20KCEXk4aXXXXXXXX_!!612263230.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/612263230/T2ceGEXj8aXXXXXXXX_!!612263230.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px\" alt=\"\" /><img align=\"absMiddle\" src=\"http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/612263230/T2H7G9XhJbXXXXXXXX_!!612263230.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; width: 300px; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px\" alt=\"\" /></div>','images/201308/thumb_img/3955_thumb_G_1375774682724.jpg','images/201308/goods_img/3955_G_1375774682071.jpg','images/201308/source_img/3955_G_1375774682434.jpg','1','','1','1','0','0','1374997873','100','0','1','0','1','0','0','1375774682','32','','0','0','0','');
