INSERT INTO necs_goods VALUES('3973','172','ECS003973','微星X79A-GD65(8D)','+','57','0','','100','0.000','0.00','2290.00','0.00','0','0','1','ATX（标准型） X79','','<p style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(64,64,64); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255,0,0)\">X79芯片组主要特性：</span>支持第二代LGA 2011 架构的Intel Core i7 处理器，支持 4 通道 DDR3 1066/1333/1600/1800*/2133*/2400* (OC)内存, 最高可支持达 64GB 内存容量，3个PCI Express x16(总线规格3.0)，支持SATA III 6GB,USB 3.0,HD Audio !</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(64,64,64); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">前一段时间，来自美国的知名极限超频玩家Turn&amp;Burn，使用<a style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: \">微星</a><a style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: \">X79A-GD65(8D)</a>，成功将<span style=\"background-color: rgb(255,0,255)\">IntelCorei7-3930K</span><a style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: \"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255,0,255)\">处理器</span></a><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255,0,255)\">频率超频至5.83GHz的惊人成绩。超频幅度高达182%，创下世界最高SandyBridge-E处理器频率的纪录</span>。作为顶级<a style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: \">X79</a>芯片组的<a style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: \">产品</a>，微星X79A-GD65(8D)<a style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: \">主板</a>定位为高端发烧级玩家。目前市场上的报价是2999元。下面我们就来具体了解一下这款超频破纪录的主板。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(64,64,64); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><br style=\"font-size: 0px; line-height: 0\" />\r\n<img alt=\"打破SNB-E超频世界纪录 微星X79主板推荐\" src=\"http://2e.zol-img.com.cn/product/87_450x337/860/ceE2zYFTWmO02.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"337\" style=\"border-top: black 0px solid; border-right: black 0px solid; vertical-align: top; border-bottom: black 0px solid; border-left: black 0px solid\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(64,64,64); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">处理器供电方面，由于SNB-E处理器庞大的处理器核心，微星X79A-GD65(8D)主板采用了12相处理器供电解决方案，使用了高质量钽电容用料，Mosfet部分提供了热管<a style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: \">散热器</a>。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(64,64,64); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"打破SNB-E超频世界纪录 微星X79主板推荐\" src=\"http://2c.zol-img.com.cn/product/87_450x337/864/ceyj6mSr4Vuo.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"337\" style=\"border-top: black 0px solid; border-right: black 0px solid; vertical-align: top; border-bottom: black 0px solid; border-left: black 0px solid\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(64,64,64); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><br />\r\n微星X79A-GD65(8D)支持四通道<a style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: \">内存</a>，提供8条内存插槽，最大扩展容量达到惊人的128GB。内存插槽采用了单卡扣设计，方便用户拆卸内存。每组内存插槽提供2相独立供电，为后期内存超频提供基础。磁盘方面，主板提供了多大8个SATA3磁盘接口，支持多种RAID模式。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(64,64,64); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"打破SNB-E超频世界纪录 微星X79主板推荐\" src=\"http://2f.zol-img.com.cn/product/87_450x337/867/cerZP6uL6gvy2.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"337\" style=\"border-top: black 0px solid; border-right: black 0px solid; vertical-align: top; border-bottom: black 0px solid; border-left: black 0px solid\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(64,64,64); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">基于板型的良好优势，主板提供了5条PCI-Ex16插槽，支持双卡x16+x16模式下的AMDCrossFire和NVIDIASLI。在主板底部，主板还提供了微星易超频精灵功能和开机微动开关，方便用户裸机操作。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(64,64,64); padding-bot