 black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; border-right: black 1px solid\" /><br />\r\n金河田网神2号2052机箱电源</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　金河田网神5号机箱配有网吧专用宽幅电源劲霸ATX-S388，这款电源作了节电优化。由于网吧配置存储数量较少，并且没有功能配件，额定250W的功率足够网吧主流配置的供电需求。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong>编辑点评：</strong>金河田网神2号系列网吧机箱使用报警器设计，加上测板上的机箱锁，起到双重保护作用。机箱做工细致，用料充足，并且价格合理，适合网吧用户使用。</p>','images/201307/thumb_img/4059_thumb_G_1375094375287.jpg','images/201307/goods_img/4059_G_1375094375976.jpg','images/201307/source_img/4059_G_1375094375212.jpg','1','','1','1','0','0','1375094375','100','0','0','0','0','0','0','1376888229','21','','0','0','0','');
